{"tid":2508406,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"第一次接觸70年代嘅韓國電視劇","createTime":"2021-04-28T17:37:11.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-29T03:19:38.000Z","uid":52429,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bae2f770ec907e25f30a9b34b5a0736876f7ec54","tid":2508406,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:37:11.000Z","msg":"《戰友》（韓語：전우；英語：Comrades）是韓國KBS電視台於1975年6月29日－1978年4月8日起播出的連續劇，該劇在1983年首次翻拍，而2010年因紀念韓戰爆發60週年再次翻拍。故事講述在韓戰中，9個韓國士兵為國家出生入死的故事。<br />\n<br />\n70年代嘅韓劇仲係黑白製作<br />\n而且以韓戰為主<br />\n好似呢套《戰友》咁<br />\n由1975年拍到1978年<br />\n就拍咗大約200集<br />\n<br />\n主題曲<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/n1cbWmYxLH0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fn1cbWmYxLH0&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=8ebc8eaf\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/n1cbWmYxLH0</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PutXR4ZB3ks\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPutXR4ZB3ks&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=5d31cb46\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PutXR4ZB3ks</a><br />\n<br />\n1977年播嘅其中三集<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/AQ06y8rOuV8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FAQ06y8rOuV8&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=035e72d3\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/AQ06y8rOuV8</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/i8TqntQ4T7o\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fi8TqntQ4T7o&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=27504174\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/i8TqntQ4T7o</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/hk9MIBaU3ag\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2Fhk9MIBaU3ag&d=DgCTbN7XbHZJJfbPUwNNzc5RZDHrhPshgzcG8Nqr5vw%3D&h=936fee64\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/hk9MIBaU3ag</a>"},{"pid":"83b31b278ce64ea89a0b558a2878b93053a1d441","tid":2508406,"uid":52429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-28T17:43:41.000Z","msg":"<im